{"tid":812922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天兩度去信美國     王國興：吳三桂所為","createTime":"2018-09-10T04:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T15:31:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"91dbc6d42f1de2f94b4a8bd19a8bbe998158eddd","tid":812922,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"香港民族黨發言人陳浩天繼前往「香港外國記者會」煽「獨」後，又先後去信美國總統特朗普及美國國會，要求美國干預及制裁香港和內地。立法會前議員、「廿三萬監察」發言人王國興對陳浩天的行為感到極之忿怒，撰文怒斥其行為是「吳三桂所為」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n王國興指責，陳浩天「大言不慚一再去信美國總統『引兵入關』，要借美力干預制裁香港和內地。如此赤裸裸出賣國家，出賣香港的吳三桂所為」，王國興認為，陳浩天事件是「皇帝的新衣」的最新香港版。王國興並質疑，保安局打算以社團條例取締「香港民族黨」，卻不斷延後申期限，「是軟弱執法的可笑例證」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9F/37758/-%E8%B3%A3%E6%B8%AF%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9%E5%85%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%A3%E6%B8%AF%E8%B3%A3%E5%9C%8B-%E7%8E%8B%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%88-%E5%90%B3%E4%B8%89%E6%A1%82%E6%89%80%E7%82%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%2594%259F%2F37758%2F-%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2588%2588-%25E5%2590%25B3%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25A1%2582%25E6%2589%2580%25E7%2582%25BA&d=FzJLSKu%2FbYC3KX6Cw1qdVIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e0702d26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9F/37758/-%E8%B3%A3%E6%B8%AF%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9%E5%85%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%A3%E6%B8%AF%E8%B3%A3%E5%9C%8B-%E7%8E%8B%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%88-%E5%90%B3%E4%B8%89%E6%A1%82%E6%89%80%E7%82%BA</a>"},{"pid":"af7ba6c35a77730f7bb857dbdb5af237859d79a3","tid":812922,"uid":184679,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"